# Goal Description
Transform the current analytics-centric Smart HR UI into a Case-Centric product. Analytics will now produce "Signals" that feed into "Alerts", which are then converted into "Cases" spanning a full lifecycle (Open → Assign → Act → Monitor → Measure → Close).

## Proposed Changes

### Routing and Navigation
#### [MODIFY] [client/src/App.tsx](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/App.tsx)
- Add new routes: `/dashboard/alerts`, `/dashboard/cases`, `/dashboard/data-quality`.
- Ensure legacy routes (like `/dashboard/interventions`) still work or redirect appropriately.

#### [MODIFY] [client/src/components/layout/_nav.ts](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/components/layout/_nav.ts)
