### New Core Centers

#### [NEW] `client/src/pages/dashboard/AlertsPage.tsx`
- New top-level page for the Alerts Center.

#### [NEW] `client/src/components/features/alerts/...`
- Add `AlertsList.tsx` for viewing All, Unread, and High Severity alerts.
- Add `AlertDrawer.tsx` with tabs for Summary, Signal, Action, and "Open Case" behavior.

#### [NEW] `client/src/pages/dashboard/CasesPage.tsx`
- New top-level page for Case Management.

#### [NEW] `client/src/components/features/cases/...`
- Add `CasesList.tsx` grouping cases by Open, In Progress, Review, and Closed.
- Add `CaseDetailsDrawer.tsx` (or Page) with tabs: Summary, Signals, Actions, Monitoring, Impact, Timeline.
- Add `useCases.ts` to manage local mock state/persistence using `localStorage`.

#### [NEW] `client/src/pages/dashboard/DataQualityPage.tsx`
- New top-level page for Data Quality.

#### [NEW] `client/src/components/features/data-quality/...`
- Implement `DataQualityDashboard.tsx` for missing/conflicting value scans, policy controls, and logs.

